NEW YORK CREDIT MEN'S ASSOCIATION, Appellee, v. Jack HASENBERG, Appellant. No. 55. Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. Oct. 30, 1939. Wegman & Climenko, of New York City (Jesse Climenko, of New York City, of counsel), for appellant. J. Jacob Hahn and Hahn & Golin, all of New York City, for appellee.

Before L. HAND, AUGUSTUS N. HAND, and CLARK, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Order, 26 F.Supp. 877, affirmed.
